    <note>Liu(2) Huanghou [20453] She was orphaned young and was raised by her maternal kin, who must have been Chengdu, Huayang residents since she is identified as a Huayang person noted by the Sichuanese for her beauty. She entered the palace in 983 at age 14 and was invested as empress in 1012. CBD has her being invested as Meiren on the accession of Zhenzong, but HSSCGY, 3.1b dates this appointment in 1004. CBD, 5, 3969.</note>
